WEBVTT

00:06.753 --> 00:09.244
<i>In New York City's
war on crime,</i>

00:09.323 --> 00:11.382
<i>the worst criminal offenders
are pursued</i>

00:11.458 --> 00:14.291
<i>by the detectives
of the Major Case Squad.</i>

00:14.361 --> 00:16.329
<i>These are their stories.</i>

00:18.332 --> 00:22.666
And I'm pleased to announce that the
contract for Julius Seven is ours.

00:28.108 --> 00:32.875
Manufacturing this new component will
improve the security of our country.

00:32.946 --> 00:35.813
In charge of this
project will be Don,

00:39.920 --> 00:42.650
With the support
and assistance of Paul.

00:48.562 --> 00:50.427
You must feel
so disappointed.

00:50.497 --> 00:53.933
Anyway, did you notice that the
registration on your car expired last week?

00:54.000 --> 00:55.968
I was lucky I didn't
get a ticket.

00:56.036 --> 00:58.664
<i>If you come home by 5:00,
I'll go to the DMV.</i>

00:59.005 --> 01:01.200
Here, Mom, I did my exercise.

01:02.476 --> 01:05.001
<i>I can't leave early today,
I got to...</i>

01:05.679 --> 01:07.408
Doreen, I got to go.

01:11.852 --> 01:14.184
Mom, I can't
find my blue jacket.

01:14.254 --> 01:16.620
Okay. Honey, you ready to go?

01:18.859 --> 01:23.296
It's not gonna fit, Mom. Too bad
you can't sit up front like me.

01:23.363 --> 01:24.921
This is just
an exception, Adam.

01:24.998 --> 01:28.297
Why do I have to sit in
my car seat? It's no fair.

01:28.368 --> 01:31.303
I wish the world was fair,
Billy. I really do.

